    transliteration: 'śauryaṃ tejo dhṛtirdākṣyaṃ yuddhe cāpyapalāyanam | dānamīśvarabhāvaśca kṣātraṃ karma svabhāvajam ||',
    englishTranslation: 'Valour, radiance, fortitude, skill, not fleeing in battle, generosity, and the capacity to govern — these are the natural duties of the Kshatriya.',
